<div class="container"> 
<h3>Thank you in advance for taking 5 minutes of your time filling out this survey</h3>
<%= form_tag "/surveys", method: :post do %>
<ol>
  <li><b>Email: </b><input type="email" name="student_email"></li>
  <p><li>At campus did your tutoring session take place?</li></p>
  <p>
  <% Location.all.each do |location| %>
  <input type="radio" required name="question1" value="<%= location.name %>"> <%= location.name %>
  <% end %>
  </p>
  <p><li>What subject were you tutored today</li></p>
  <% Subject.all.each do |subject| %>
  <input type="radio" required name="question2" value="<%= subject.department %>"> <%= subject.department %>
  <% end %>
  <p><li>How did you first hear about Learning center?</li></p>
  <input type="radio" required name="question3" value="Teacher">Teacher
  <input type="radio" required name="question3" value="Librarian"> Librarian
  <input type="radio" required name="question3" value="Fellow Student"> Fellow student
  <input type="radio" required name="question3" value="College website"> College website
  <input type="radio" required name="question3" value="other"> Other
  <p><li>Are you a</li></p>
  <input type="radio" required name="question4" value="Freshman">Freshman
  <input type="radio" required name="question4" value="Sophomore">Sophomore
  <input type="radio" required name="question4" value="Junior">Junior
  <input type="radio" required name="question4" value="Senior">Senior
  <input type="radio" required name="question4" value="Grad Student">Grad Student
  <input type="radio" required name="question4" value="Other">Other
  <p><li>My tutor was knowledgeable about the subject being tutored</li></p>
  <input type="radio" required name="question5" value="Strongly agree">Strongly agree
  <input type="radio" required name="question5" value="Agree">Agree
  <input type="radio" required name="question5" value="Neutral">Neutral
  <input type="radio" required name="question5" value="Disagree">Disagree
  <input type="radio" required name="question5" value="Strongly disagree">Strongly disagree
  <p><li>After my session I feel more comfortable about the subject under discussion</li></p>
  <input type="radio" required name="question6" value="Strongly agree">Strongly agree
  <input type="radio" required name="question6" value="Agree">Agree
  <input type="radio" required name="question6" value="Neutral">Neutral
  <input type="radio" required name="question6" value="Disagree">Disagree
  <input type="radio" required name="question6" value="Strongly disagree">Strongly disagree
  <p><li>Based on my experience today, I will recommend the learning center service to another student</li></p>
  <input type="radio" required name="question7" value="Strongly agree">Strongly agree
  <input type="radio" required name="question7" value="Agree">Agree
  <input type="radio" required name="question7" value="Neutral">Neutral
  <input type="radio" required name="question7" value="Disagree">Disagree
  <input type="radio" required name="question7" value="Strongly disagree">Strongly disagree
  <p><li>Over all my experience at the learning center was</li></p>
  <input type="radio" required name="question8" value="Excellent">Excellent
  <input type="radio" required name="question8" value="Good">Good
  <input type="radio" required name="question8" value="Fair">Fair
  <input type="radio" required name="question8" value="Poor">Poor
 disagree
 <p><li>Why did come to this tutoring session today?</li> </p>
  <textarea required name="question10" icols="60" rows="4"></textarea>
  <p><li>What did learn that was new during this tutoring session?</li></p>
  <textarea required name="question11" icols="60" rows="4"></textarea>
  <p><li> What would do next to ensure that you do well in this class?</li></p>
  <textarea required name="question12" icols="60" rows="4"></textarea>
  <p><li>What else could we do to help you do well in this class</li></p>
    <textarea required name="question9" icols="60" rows="4"></textarea>
  <p><li>Additional comments</li></p>
  <textarea required name="question13" icols="60" rows="4"></textarea>
</ol>
 <button class="btn btn-success" style="margin-top: 10px; margin-left:50px;">Send survey </button>
<% end %>
</div>
